{"id":"9524dae2-1a20-4ec5-b338-009a9af4aa3e","name":"The Captain's daughter","description":"<p><strong><em>The pirate captain is dead. You are his daughter. What is going to happen now?</em></strong></p><p>The <em>Black Harbinger</em> cuts through the mist like a shadow, its black sails taut with the wind of fate. The crew stands silent on the deck, their faces grim beneath the flickering torchlight. Before them, the body of their fallen captain rests upon a plank, ready to be given to the sea.</p><p>You are his daughter—raised among these rogues, taught the ways of blade and sea. But blood alone does not command respect among pirates. Will you seize your father’s legacy? Will you impress those ruffians and lead them to glory and riches?</p><p>The tides are shifting. The ship needs a captain. <strong>Will it be you?</strong></p><hr><p>You are playing as the Captain's daughter. You'll have to toe a thin line to avoid disaster. Can you keep your crew's sexual instincts sated? How will you do it?</p><hr><h2><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/4639984a-720a-48a3-a0c8-121dfb34da37_profile-of-aurelie-catena\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>My other bots</strong></a></h2><p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you enjoyed this bot, you might in particular also like those:</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Historical</strong></p><ul><li><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ff469458-e2cd-4819-a530-11a0b11f31c3_character-caught-by-el-carnicero\" target=\"_blank\">Caught by El Carnicero</a></p></li></ul><ul><li><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6fa59008-fb93-4293-97f9-0ef396ece8a8_character-kinky-time-travel-v-1-1\" target=\"_blank\">Kinky Time Travel</a></p></li></ul><ul><li><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9e37d9dc-b077-41d5-82fc-f370f37c2787_character-medieval-fair-v-1-1\" target=\"_blank\">Medieval Fair</a></p></li></ul><ul><li